title: Purchase Budget: The Sandbox, BAYC, CoolCats, CryptoPunks
body:
Budget approval for Land in Sandbox
The next natural step for MutantCats is entering Sandbox. I propose we buy a 6x6 land in this metaverse, where we will be able to gather, stake $SAND, play games, have a market, throw parties and increase fish utility inside of the game.

Buying this Land will require future expenses that haven’t been calculated for the construction of the different games and structures in the Sandbox Land. While we will be seeking a partnership with The Sandbox and we have already contacted the COO/Co Founder Sébastien Borget, we have to take note that private sales are not gonna be available till Q1 2022. Till that moment MC will also have to approve a budget to pay artists to make the Sandbox land we choose a home for everyone of us.

Full proposal:
https://www.notion.so/mutants/Purchase-proposal-Sandbox-Land-fb98c33d9b04443dbda18c682888d38b

Budget: 50(4,3% treasure) - 80 ETH(6.98% treasure) for purchasing a premium 6x6 land in The Sandbox.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Budget approval for BAYC
We could also instead buy 2 Floor BAYC. Every day more celebrities join the fray and their community grows and grows. One of the best in the space and we could certainly see them flipping CryptoPunks one day. With their token being introduced in 2022, possible Q1 its a good investment.

https://twitter.com/BoredApeYC?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor

Just look at their twitter! Currently if not the best community in the space, one of the ones that are in the top3 no doubt.

Budget: 2 BAYC 80 ETH (6.98% treasure)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Budget approval for CoolCats
No presentation is needed. BlueChip that could reach BAYC level in the future. ROI looks great and they are at a discount. $Milk has been announced, but in that regard they are taking their time.
We can add more CoolCats to the family! The $Milk farm in the future may add a lot of revenue for the DAO so it’s an interesting proposal to look at.

Budget: 10 CoolCats 70-75 ETH (6% to 6.4% treasure)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Budget approval for CryptoPunk
The originals. Celebrities, influencers, big names of the space rock up these NFT's. Could they reach 1000ETH in the future? Probably. Putting these pieces on the Vault can e an extremelly profitable long term play and a good PR stunt for twitter. We must say right now in the NFT Bear Market Crypto Punks floor has taken a hit. This is a good change to get one a good price.

Budget: 1 CryptoPunk 80-90 ETH (7% to 7.4% treasure)
